title: Raising Standards & Owning Our True Selves
description:
This week Tasia opens up about her relationship with anti-depressants and reflects on how much she's grown over the course of her mental health journey and Camo talks laser hair removal and clapping back at at close-minded family members. Together they discuss the importance of finding non-transactional friends and partners and offer advice on how to empower yourself to own who you are!
Go to GoodAmerican.com/UNFAZED and use code UNFAZED at checkout for $50 off your first pair of jeans!
